cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GR 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper proposes a method for object pose estimation from RGB-D images using template matching and feature maps. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the proposed method can be applied to robotic systems for object manipulation and grasping. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper uses machine learning techniques for template generation and pose estimation. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also possible as the paper uses a balanced pose tree and memory rearrangement for efficient template matching. 
- cs.GR (Graphics) is less likely but still possible as the paper uses 3D CAD models for template generation.
